Package cdx.opencdx.commons.data

Class OpenCDXIdentifier

java.lang.Object
cdx.opencdx.commons.data.OpenCDXIdentifier
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<OpenCDXIdentifier>
public class OpenCDXIdentifier extends Object implements Comparable<OpenCDXIdentifier>, Serializable
OpenCDXIdentifier is a wrapper around ObjectId that provides a more descriptive name and implements Comparable.
